LingBash is a lanaguage learning tool designed to help users with vocabulary and reading comprehension. 
Try to read wikipedia articles in your target language without viewing translations.
The articles are displayed section-by-section. If you reach a section you don't fully understand, you can view a translation into your native language.
Try to read as much as you can without translating!


This demo page provides a preview of it's core functionality. 
To view translations, you must first sign in or continue as a guest. 
Then, in preferences, select your target language (the language you are learning) and your home language. 
Finally, simply search for articles in your target language! 

